<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Populous" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Populous,</orth> well peopled: <bibl n="shak. r2 5.5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 V, 5, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.360" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 360</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 1.1.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 1, 77</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 4.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 64</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 4.6.197" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 6, 197</bibl>. == composed of many people, numerous: <cit><quote>the dust . . . raised by your p. troops,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ant 3.6.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 6, 50</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>